26 make 211 services available throughout Indiana. The fund shall be
27 administered by the office of the secretary.
28 (b) The fund consists of the following:
29 (1) All money appropriated to the fund by the general assembly.
30 (2) Funds received from the federal government for the support
31 of 211 services in Indiana.
32 (3) Investment earnings, including interest, on money in the fund.
33 (4) Money from any other source, including gifts and grants.
